29:39.760 --> 29:41.400
"The recorder. Where's the recorder?"

29:41.480 --> 29:43.800
-My arm was here...
-I'm sorry.

29:43.960 --> 29:45.840
-I'm sorry.
-Antonio was petrified.

29:45.920 --> 29:49.280
But at least my drinks were on the house.
So we're at peace now.

29:51.360 --> 29:53.400
-Everything's fine, thank you.
-Fine.

29:53.560 --> 29:55.480
-Fine.
