Fucking awful, I'd say.

30:12.880 --> 30:13.760
God...

30:14.080 --> 30:16.720
Excuse me, but... I...

30:17.480 --> 30:20.040
No, the emergency was...

30:21.480 --> 30:24.080
my ex-husband had taken my daughter and...

30:24.760 --> 30:27.440
Well, he's got a restraining order
