32:26.200 --> 32:29.240
I've seen it on TV.
And pieces of glass... It's all right.

32:29.320 --> 32:31.480
-Okay, okay.
-Leave it there.

32:31.680 --> 32:34.920
We'll cover the bleeding
and see how you progress, okay?

32:35.360 --> 32:36.240
-Yes.
-Calm down.

32:42.160 --> 32:43.040
Okay.

32:45.480 --> 32:46.720
Okay, okay.

32:48.000 --> 32:49.760
Okay, okay.

32:50.120 --> 32:51.000
Okay.

33:00.800 --> 33:01.840
Fine.

33:02.160 --> 33:07.040
Just like when we were kids
and played that Operation game...

33:13.160 --> 33:14.040
Okay.

