more contraindications than a bullet.

34:31.000 --> 34:32.240
I was thinking of the baby.

34:34.360 --> 34:35.400
You're right.

34:36.040 --> 34:37.840
Okay, okay.

34:38.560 --> 34:41.920
I'll read the pamphlet
and see what we do, okay?

34:48.720 --> 34:49.600
