No.

36:30.720 --> 36:32.760
Hey. Have you got more noodles?

36:38.480 --> 36:40.480
Not noodles. I have some rice.

36:42.360 --> 36:43.400
It's all right.

36:50.880 --> 36:51.760
Moscow.

36:57.360 --> 36:59.880
Moscow, what are you doing? Hey!

37:01.080 --> 37:02.520
What the fuck are you doing?

37:04.040 --> 37:05.320
Tokyo, what's up?

37:05.400 --> 37:07.560
-I don't know.
-Don't open the doors!

37:07.640 --> 37:08.520
Moscow!

37:11.560 --> 37:14.120
-They're opening the doors.
-Get ready.

37:14.200 --> 37:16.760
-Come on, come on!
-In your places.

37:19.480 --> 37:20.520
Don't move!

37:21.400 --> 37:22.280
Snipers.

37:22.360 --> 37:24.480
-"Alpha 1 positioned.
-Alpha 2 positioned.

37:24.560 --> 37:26.040
Alpha 3 positioned."

37:27.400 --> 37:28.960
On the floor! Everyone!

37:29.040 --> 37:30.280
On the floor! Now!

37:32.600 --> 37:33.920
I have a shot.

37:34.000 --> 37:35.440
-In three, two, one.
-Dad!

37:35.560 --> 37:38.120
-Cover your face! Cover your face!
-Let me out.

37:38.280 --> 37:40.080
-They're not wearing masks.
-"They're wrestling."

37:40.160 --> 37:42.120
-No, dad.
-I have to get out.

37:42.280 --> 37:44.320
-Record it.
-"I can't see their faces."

37:44.480 --> 37:46.320
-I have to get out.
-Out? Why?

37:46.400 --> 37:47.920
"Sir, I have a shot."

37:49.120 --> 37:52.520
It's my fault. You shouldn't be here.
You shouldn't have killed anyone.

37:52.760 --> 37:54.920
-"Waiting for the order.
-Have I got the green light, sir?"

37:57.680 --> 37:59.520
-Let me out.
-You want to turn yourself in

37:59.600 --> 38:02.760
-so you can be the patsy.
-"We don't know if they're robbers.

38:02.920 --> 38:04.440
Have I got the green light, sir?"

38:05.680 --> 38:07.720
-Let me out.
-I didn't kill her.

38:09.400 --> 38:11.160
-Let me out.
-I didn't kill her.

38:11.560 --> 38:13.200
She's hidden.

38:17.320 --> 38:19.600
"The doors are closing, sir.
Three seconds.

38:19.680 --> 38:21.760
-Doors closed.
-Don't shoot."

38:25.680 --> 38:26.680
Jesus!

38:29.120 --> 38:31.320
-Let me out.
-We're getting out, dad.

38:31.480 --> 38:33.640
Outside, so you can breathe fresh air.

38:33.720 --> 38:35.240
-I need some air.
-Yes.

38:43.280 --> 38:45.160
I'm so sorry that you had gone through...

38:48.080 --> 38:51.080
Through an experience so...

38:52.240 --> 38:56.840
Well, if you need some kind of help,
I can give you...

38:57.760 --> 39:00.600
A phone always at your disposal,
a bodyguard with glasses...

39:03.000 --> 39:04.960
I'm sorry. I shouldn't have joked
about something like that.

39:05.040 --> 39:06.680
-I'm a jerk.
-No, don't worry.

39:06.760 --> 39:10.040
I apologise.
But I see you and... And it doesn't fit.

39:10.120 --> 39:13.360
It's not what I imagine
when I think about...

39:13.520 --> 39:16.720
About what? A battered woman?

39:19.960 --> 39:21.400
Because I've got a gun, right?

39:23.520 --> 39:24.520
Listen,

39:25.680 --> 39:29.360
the reality is that...
it doesn't start with a smack.

39:30.600 --> 39:34.040
In that case,
nobody would be with a violent man.

39:36.280 --> 39:37.640
It's the other way round.

39:38.840 --> 39:39.720
You're...

39:40.440 --> 39:44.120
You fall in love
with a charming and intelligent man...

39:45.040 --> 39:47.400
who makes you feel
the centre of the universe.

39:48.320 --> 39:52.240
And when he asks you
to change your profile picture

39:52.320 --> 39:55.320
and use a picture of your daughter,
you think it's tender.

39:56.920 --> 40:00.360
And when he tells you
not to wear a miniskirt to work,

40:00.840 --> 40:04.280
you think: "I'm a woman who works

40:04.360 --> 40:08.560
in a men's world,
he's actually protecting me."

40:11.120 --> 40:15.280
And then one day... he raises his voice...

40:15.880 --> 40:19.840
-You don't have to tell me.
-Yes, yes. I need it.

40:21.000 --> 40:22.120
Look, it's like...

40:23.200 --> 40:25.360
It's like going down steps
little by little.

40:25.480 --> 40:29.160
Like in those horror films
where somebody goes down to the basement

40:29.240 --> 40:33.240
and everybody thinks:
"Don't go downstairs. Don't do it."

40:34.720 --> 40:35.680
But you do it.

40:38.120 --> 40:39.560
That's where I got the first slap.

40:41.600 --> 40:43.960
And then the second, and the third...

40:46.120 --> 40:47.600
And finally I got the divorce.

40:52.280 --> 40:53.400
Didn't you report him?

40:55.600 --> 40:58.000
No. He was a police officer,

40:58.560 --> 41:03.800
the most popular guy in the station,
and I just wanted to lose sight of him.

41:06.280 --> 41:11.200
I guess... I was ashamed
to sit down in front of my boss

41:12.120 --> 41:15.760
and tell him about a year and a half
of humiliation and blows.

41:18.080 --> 41:20.520
I've got a 9mm HK in my holster,

41:20.600 --> 41:24.760
but... I really don't fucking know
how to take care of myself.

41:26.480 --> 41:27.440
Don't say that.

41:28.600 --> 41:33.480
But... the real drama
came some months later.

41:35.280 --> 41:38.000
Because my sister fell in love with him.

41:43.160 --> 41:46.720
They started going out, and travelling.

41:48.240 --> 41:49.640
And then I reported him,

41:51.080 --> 41:52.440
late and without evidence.

41:57.320 --> 41:59.960
Because I didn't want my sister
to get into that hell.

42:01.000 --> 42:01.920
Do you understand?

42:03.920 --> 42:07.960
But, sure, I only seemed to be
a pathological jealous woman

42:08.040 --> 42:09.600
making a fake complaint.

42:11.760 --> 42:14.040
"See? The inspector
didn't report him back then

42:14.560 --> 42:16.800
but she does now he's with her sister."

42:17.080 --> 42:21.160
But, Raquel, the police or the judges

42:21.240 --> 42:23.720
must believe you,
it's impossible not to believe you.

42:24.840 --> 42:26.920
Raquel, now I've felt
the emotion and the helplessness.

42:27.000 --> 42:28.400
There must be someone who can help you.

42:28.560 --> 42:30.840
-Someone. Who's going to help me?
-Me.

42:34.240 --> 42:37.800
Sorry, I don't know
how I could help you, but...

42:41.960 --> 42:42.840
Thanks.

42:46.640 --> 42:47.520
Raquel.

42:49.840 --> 42:51.120
-Raquel.
-Ángel.

42:51.440 --> 42:52.880
There's movement in the building.

42:52.960 --> 42:55.640
They opened the door for a few seconds
and there was a brawl.

42:55.720 --> 42:57.640
-We think it was with a hostage.
-Let's go.

43:12.920 --> 43:15.680
Listen, I want you to know
this is not a threat,

43:16.280 --> 43:19.200
but a personal favour
I'm asking you, not as a robber.

43:19.800 --> 43:22.040
I want you to put on the masks, the hoods

43:22.440 --> 43:25.200
and to get out to the terraced roof
without any signals or silly things.

43:25.440 --> 43:27.280
Only for 10 minutes, okay?

43:27.560 --> 43:30.680
You go out, have some fresh air
and come back, all right?

43:33.200 --> 43:36.320
What do you want, to distract the police?

43:36.440 --> 43:37.840
The police is already distracted,

43:37.920 --> 43:40.480
so leave them alone
and don't ruffle any feathers.

43:41.360 --> 43:44.800
We're bait. They're using us as bait.

43:44.880 --> 43:46.800
-What's that?
-They're throwing us to the wolves

43:46.880 --> 43:48.600
and meanwhile
they'll escape using another door.

43:48.680 --> 43:50.680
We're getting out due to humanity,

43:52.160 --> 43:56.280
because one of our mates needs to breathe,
and I won't tell you again.

43:59.000 --> 44:00.000
Don't move.

44:04.000 --> 44:05.640
What fucking world are we living in?

44:06.480 --> 44:08.840
Nobody's willing to do anything
for anybody, right?

44:09.240 --> 44:13.520
One of us has an anxiety attack
and you only think that you're a bait.

44:14.560 --> 44:15.960
Nothing's gonna happen.

44:16.320 --> 44:19.200
Nothing's gonna happen,
because I'm going out with you.

44:19.840 --> 44:21.680
Why did he have an anxiety attack?

44:22.400 --> 44:24.480
Due to shots. It was the shots, right?

44:24.560 --> 44:27.920
It was the shots. Who did you kill?
Who did you kill?

44:29.680 --> 44:31.120
Open your mouth, Arturo.

44:33.920 --> 44:35.760
Open your fucking mouth, Arturo.

44:36.280 --> 44:37.560
Open your mouth.

44:39.080 --> 44:42.440
Now raise your left hand
if you're going to keep on fucking around.

44:43.000 --> 44:46.120
If you're going to keep your mouth shut,
raise your right hand.

44:51.400 --> 44:52.280
Fine.

44:53.120 --> 44:55.040
Denver, stop it, now.

44:55.760 --> 44:56.640
Stop it.

45:00.960 --> 45:03.040
Stop goofing around, please.

45:04.760 --> 45:07.080
-He wasn't a hostage.
-Why do you say that?

45:08.240 --> 45:10.080
Because, unless
they're Gandhi's disciples,

45:10.160 --> 45:11.760
they'd never let a hostage get so far

45:11.920 --> 45:15.320
without shooting him in the back.
One of them wanted to turn himself in.

45:19.600 --> 45:20.840
Now, dad.

45:22.000 --> 45:23.200
Breathe some air.

45:26.280 --> 45:28.080
You don't need to do this for me.

45:30.200 --> 45:31.920
I remember when mum left,

45:33.120 --> 45:34.680
you had trouble breathing,

45:35.560 --> 45:38.120
you went out to the balcony
to try to do it every night.

45:38.360 --> 45:40.760
So, it doesn't matter,
you're going out there,

45:40.840 --> 45:43.800
breathe some fresh air
and when you're calm, we'll get back.

45:43.880 --> 45:47.800
Everyone with the masks and the hoods on.
Arturito, close to me.

