46:14.760 --> 46:16.600
-Dad, calm down.
-Okay.

46:16.760 --> 46:19.160
Look, it's a fucking great day.

46:19.240 --> 46:21.320
-Yes.
-It's very sunny, huh?

46:21.400 --> 46:23.040
Breathe and relax.

46:23.200 --> 46:25.600
"It's a big group.
They keep on walking on the roof.

46:25.680 --> 46:27.520
