Keep me posted of everything.

46:51.040 --> 46:53.720
"They keep on walking.
They're getting to the edge."

46:53.800 --> 46:57.360
If you don't start having a cool head,
forget about the millions, Acapulco

46:57.440 --> 47:00.000
and the garden full of children,
because you'll screw all up.

47:01.400 --> 47:04.720
You only have to do one thing:
be professionals.

47:07.680 --> 47:09.560
Doesn't this seem professional to you?

47:12.000 --> 47:14.120
-Precious.
-No, not precious.

47:14.720 --> 47:17.680
A fucking note
better than the ones in the bank.

47:18.120 --> 47:22.160
They can't even trace it. A work of art.

47:23.800 --> 47:26.640
-And you know why?
-Enlighten me, Nairobi.

47:31.160 --> 47:33.800
Because it's been made with care.

47:35.920 --> 47:37.520
I'm a professional.

47:38.280 --> 47:39.680
But I don't know what to do

47:39.760 --> 47:42.440
when your father has the heebie-jeebies
in the middle of this mess.

47:43.080 --> 47:44.680
Are you a robber before a son?

47:45.760 --> 47:46.720
Huh, Berlin?

47:47.640 --> 47:49.080
Before a human being?

47:52.920 --> 47:55.240
For a shithead like you maybe yes,

47:56.160 --> 47:58.240
but... I don't know.

48:05.480 --> 48:07.640
-Didn't you kill that girl?
-No.

48:08.160 --> 48:09.600
-Tell me the fucking truth.
-I didn't!

48:12.480 --> 48:14.040
Berlin caught her with a phone,

48:14.680 --> 48:16.880
ordered me to kill her
and I had to shoot her,

48:16.960 --> 48:19.280
-I had no choice.
-You're talking about Mónica.

48:19.800 --> 48:20.960
You're talking about Mónica.

48:21.040 --> 48:23.040
-What are you doing?
-What did you do to Mónica?

48:23.120 --> 48:24.160
Go back to your place.

48:24.240 --> 48:26.120
This is not a courtesy call, Professor.

48:26.200 --> 48:28.880
If you want me to be frank
and not hide information from you,

48:28.960 --> 48:30.080
you should do the same.

48:31.000 --> 48:33.320
Everybody has the right
to stretch their legs.

48:34.000 --> 48:37.560
"Don't you think it's solidary of me
to let the hostages go out to breathe?"

48:38.640 --> 48:41.520
I assure it's not my intention
torturing or scaring them.

48:42.320 --> 48:44.800
"I only want
to return them safe and sound"

48:45.600 --> 48:47.520
as soon as you give me what I requested.

48:50.680 --> 48:51.600
That's all.

48:51.960 --> 48:54.560
"I repeat, they're armed,
take cover in the operation.

48:54.720 --> 48:56.120
I request instructions."

48:56.320 --> 48:58.400
-What did you do?
-Go back to your place.

48:58.480 --> 49:00.040
-Tell me where Mónica is.
-Go back.

49:00.640 --> 49:03.760
-"Something happens.
-I request instructions."

49:03.960 --> 49:07.120
You killed Mónica, Jesus.
She was innocent.

49:07.280 --> 49:10.040
-Here Condor 1. Visual of the targets.
-"I request the green light."

49:10.200 --> 49:11.560
-On your knees.
-What?

49:11.720 --> 49:14.000
-She was pregnant.
-Fucking snipers.

49:14.080 --> 49:17.000
Let them think we're hostages.
Your hands on your head.

49:17.080 --> 49:19.480
Don't play with me, stand up.
I'm talking to you.

49:19.640 --> 49:22.000
-"Something happens.
-They're bending down."

49:22.160 --> 49:25.400
-They made them kneel to execute them.
-"I need a command."

49:25.560 --> 49:26.640
There are snipers.

49:26.720 --> 49:29.240
On your knees, there are snipers.

49:29.320 --> 49:30.800
Everybody down.

49:31.160 --> 49:32.520
Go back to your place.

49:33.120 --> 49:35.240
-"A lot of movement on the roof.
-Condor 3 here."

49:35.400 --> 49:37.400
One Dalí is aiming
with his gun at another.

49:37.480 --> 49:40.880
-"I can see it clearly.
-I request instructions, sir."

49:41.240 --> 49:43.920
-I need authorization.
-"They're still on their knees, sir.

49:44.080 --> 49:45.880
-I'm waiting for instructions."
-Give me the green light.

49:46.000 --> 49:48.640
-They're running.
-I have a shot at the kidnapper.

49:48.800 --> 49:51.960
-What the fuck are you doing?
-There are snipers, jeez.

49:52.120 --> 49:53.800
-On your knees.
-"They're aiming."

49:53.960 --> 49:56.040
-Give me the green light.
-"They're going to execute them.

49:56.200 --> 49:58.080
-They're going to shoot.
-I request to open fire."

49:58.240 --> 49:59.920
Put down the gun!

50:00.360 --> 50:01.600
"They're going to kill them."

50:02.040 --> 50:03.040
Green light.

50:03.360 --> 50:05.240
Condor 3, open fire.

50:19.480 --> 50:21.360
-"Target's down, sir.
-Target's down.

50:21.800 --> 50:23.080
Target's down.

50:23.200 --> 50:24.200
We have visual."

50:24.280 --> 50:26.760
He's the manager of the factory,
Arturo Román.

50:27.240 --> 50:29.800
-Stop the fire.
-Condor 3, stop the fire.

50:29.880 --> 50:31.800
All units, stop the fire.

50:35.240 --> 50:36.640
We've shot a hostage.
